167
00:10:53,600 --> 00:10:54,840
What should we do now?

168
00:10:55,720 --> 00:10:56,320
Ma Tianhong,

169
00:10:56,320 --> 00:10:57,200
cover me for a moment.

170
00:10:58,120 --> 00:10:58,880
Me?

171
00:10:59,960 --> 00:11:01,040
What am I supposed to do?

172
00:11:02,320 --> 00:11:03,120
Ma Tianhong,

173
00:11:03,520 --> 00:11:05,520
